{"lemma":"جَوابٌ","slug":"جَوابٌ","root":"ج.#.ب","root_slug":"ج-_-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-_-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جَواب","root":"جوب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":5},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6626","n6627"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%A8%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"answer, reply","examples":[{"text":"اعلم أن لا إذا وقعت على نكرة نصبتها بغير تنوين؛ وإنما كان ذلك لما أذكره لك: إنما وضعت الأخبار جوابات للاستفهام.","english":"Al-Muqtadab"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"apodosis"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Hebrew תְּגוּבָה (təḡūḇɔ̂, tguvá)."},"ipa":["/d͡ʒa.waːb/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6626","headword_ar":"جَوَابٌ","root":"jwb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An answer, a reply,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a response,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA, *) to a letter, or writing, and to a saying, or question; and this is either affirmative or negative: (Msb:) [accord. to some, it is only after a question or demand; but this is not correct; for it is often a reply to an affirmation:] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiybapN","text_ar":"جِيبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] is syn. therewith; (S, K;) and so are ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAbapN","text_ar":"جَابَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majuwbapN","text_ar":"مَجُوبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jwAb","text_ar":"جواب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajowibapN","text_ar":"اَجْوِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawaAbaAtN","text_ar":"جَوَابَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [Hence, in grammar,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harofu jawaAbK","text_ar":"حَرْفُ جَوَابٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A responsive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"replicative, particle."},{"kind":"text","text":"And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawaAbu $aroTK","text_ar":"جَوَابُ شَرْطٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An apodosis;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"complement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"correlative, of a condition;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akoramotuka","text_ar":"اَكْرَمْتُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ino jiy^otaniY A^akoramotuka","text_ar":"اـِنْ جِيْتَنِى اَكْرَمْتُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jazaA='u $aroTK","text_ar":"جَزَا=ءُ شَرْطٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawaAbu jazaA='K","text_ar":"جَوَابُ جَزَا=ءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawaAbu qasamK","text_ar":"جَوَابُ قَسَمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"complement of an oath."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound of a bird pouncing down"},{"kind":"text","text":"from the sky. (TA from a trad.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n6627","headword_ar":"جَوَّابٌ","root":"jwb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An excellent well-digger:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] a surname given to Málik Ibn-Kaab El-Kilábee, (AO, ISk, S, K, *) because he dug not a well nor bored a rock without making it to yield water. (AO, ISk, S.) ―         -b2-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A traverser of countries; one who travels much."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaw~aAbu layolK saromadK","text_ar":"جَوَّابُ لَيْلٍ سَرْمَدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who travels all the night without sleeping."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaw~aAbN jaA^~bN","text_ar":"جَوَّابٌ جَاّبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who traverses the countries and gains wealth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaw~aAbu","text_ar":"جَوَّابُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfalaApi","text_ar":"الفَلَاةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The guide of the desert."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}